    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like there's no point in it. like i'm just wasting energy trying to bridge a gap that's never gonna close. even the quiet peace you mentioned... it feels more like just giving up on everything. is it even worth it to keep trying when you know the end result is always gonna be this feeling of isolation?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
